## Atlas region hosts 2 karst springs from 2 countries:

The karst spring discharge data of Algerian karst spring is provided by Fehdi Chemseddine (fehdi.chemseddine@univ-tebessa.dz).
The karst spring discharge data of the Moroccan karst spring is provided by Brahim Akdim (brahim.akdim@usmba.ac.ma).

For more information, please see Metadata table.
